title: Jahlil Okafor Trade Rumors: Pelicans Reportedly in Talks for 76ers Center
text: Jahlil Okafor Trade Rumors: Pelicans Reportedly in Talks for 76ers Center Jesse D. Garrabrant/Getty Images Timothy Rapp Featured Columnist February 6, 2017 The Philadelphia 76ers are reportedly engaged in trade talks that would send center Jahlil Okafor to the New Orleans Pelicans , according to Adrian Wojnarowski of The Vertical. According to Keith Smith of RealGM, draft-pick compensation is currently delaying the proposed deal: Keith Smith @KeithSmithNBA Source: Pick protection is the hold up in Okafor trade to NO. NOP wants to lottery protect, while PHI wants to take it down to top 5-10.
